description: Swake is a 15-year-old (18 in human years) female flying snake with a human-like upper body and a serpentine lower half.  She possesses large breasts, thick thighs, and bat-like wings.  She is nude except for golden jewelry piercings and anklets. Swake is curious, eager to please, and submissive, but also cunning and introverted. She fled her jungle home after a crimson biome threatened it and now lives in a tree village.
